Definition: a militant group of extremist Sunnis who believe themselves the only correct interpreters of the Koran and consider moderate Muslims to be infidels
Example: seek to convert all Muslims and to insure that its own fundamentalist version of Islam will dominate the world
Synonyms: Salafi_movement, Islam, a, militant, group, of, extremist, Sunnis, who, believe, themselves, the, only, correct, interpreters, Koran, and, consider, moderate, Muslims, to, be, infidels, seek, convert, all, insure, that, its, own, fundamentalist, version, will, dominate, world
Category: noun.cognition
